            <note props="cpp"><xref keyref="startScreenCaptureByWindowId"/> relies on WGC (Windows Graphics Capture) or GDI (Graphics Device Interface) for window sharing. On systems earlier than Windows 10 2004, WGC cannot disable mouse capture. Therefore, calling <codeph>captureMouseCursor(false)</codeph> on devices with system versions lower than Windows 10 2004 may be ineffective. See <xref keyref="ScreenCaptureParameters"/>.
This method is applicable to macOS and Windows platforms only.</note>
